        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 25 at 1:37PM EDT until July 25 at 2:00PM EDT by NWS Albany NY</headline>
        <description>At 137 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Otis, or 11
miles east of Great Barrington, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Becket, Otis, Sandisfield, Otis Wood Lanes, New Boston, Algerie Four
Corners, Bonny Rigg Corners, North Otis, Montville, Becket Center,
West New Boston, West Becket, East Otis, Cold Spring, and West Otis.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
